fm: int smallestRangeII(vector<int>& A, int K)      {         sort(A.begin(), A.end());         int diff = A.back()-A[0];         for (int i=0; i<A.size()-1; i++)         {             int MAX = max(A[i]+K, A.back()-K);             int MIN = min(A[0]+K, A[i+1]-K);             diff = min(diff, MAX-MIN);         }         return diff;     }

fm: vector<int> diStringMatch(string pattern)      {         pattern = "I" + pattern;         int n = pattern.size();                  int mx = -1;         vector<int>arr;                  for (int i=0; i<n; i++)         {             int j = i+1;             while (j<n && pattern[j]=='D')                 j++;             int count = j-i;                          for (int k= mx+count; k>=mx+1; k--)                 arr.push_back(k);                          mx = mx+count;                          i = j-1;                     }                  return arr;     }

fm: int bagOfTokensScore(vector<int>& tokens, int P)      {         sort(tokens.begin(),tokens.end());         int i = 0;         int j = tokens.size()-1;         int score = 0;         int result = 0;                  while (i<=j)         {             if (P>=tokens[i])             {                 P-=tokens[i];                 i++;                 score++;                 result = max(result,score);             }             else if (score>0)             {                 score--;                 P+=tokens[j];                 j--;             }             else                 break;         }                  return result;     }
